    KRA: { fullName: 'Krita Document', purpose: 'KRA is Krita’s native layered painting and illustration project format.', stores: 'Its ZIP-based package can preserve paint layers, vector layers, masks, animation frames, assistants, color profiles, and document metadata.', compatibility: 'Krita provides complete support; other editors may access a merged preview but not the full layer model.', uses: ['Digital painting', 'Comic illustration', 'Frame animation', 'Layered concept art'], apps: ['Krita', 'A ZIP utility for recovery only', 'Compatible preview tools'], strength: 'Preserves Krita-specific layers, masks, animation, and painting data', limitation: 'Full editability is largely limited to Krita', conversion: 'Export KRA to PNG/JPEG for final images, TIFF/PSD for supported layered interchange, or image sequences for animation. Keep the KRA master.' },
